OL,3,CProposition to decriminalise cannabis
OL,4,Cin Jersey for personal use
OL,6,FA proposition aimed at decriminalising
OL,7,Fcannabis in could be debated this year.
OL,9,FDeputy Tom Coles is drawing up a
OL,10,Fproposal that would see cannabis
OL,11,Fdecriminalised for personal use on the
OL,12,Fisland.
OL,14,FThe rules around cannabis have already
OL,15,Feased this year; repeat offenders in
OL,16,Fpossession of small amounts can be
OL,17,Fsent to their parish hall to be fined
OL,18,Frather than going through the courts.
