OL,3,CProposition to decriminalise cannabis
OL,4,Cin Jersey for personal use
OL,6,FBut this latest move would mean that
OL,7,Fany personal use of small quantities
OL,8,Fwould be decriminalised.
OL,10,FSome Jersey residents have been
OL,11,Fcalling for a change in the law for
OL,12,Fyears, such as James Bedding: a
OL,13,Fquadriplegic who has taken it for
OL,14,Fyears for medicinal and recreational
OL,15,Fpurposes.
OL,17,FHe said: "I did start as a
OL,18,Frecreational user and now I use it
OL,19,Fmedically. I consume cannabis in a
OL,20,Fvapouriser to help with my spasms.
