OL,3,CProposition to decriminalise cannabis
OL,4,Cin Jersey for personal use
OL,6,F"It can really aid your life if you
OL,7,Fconsume it in the correct manner and
OL,8,Fit's regulated."
OL,10,FDeputy Tom Coles said, "There is a lot
OL,11,Fof evidence that now shows that if
OL,12,Fpeople are given space, time, and
OL,13,Fsupport, eventually they'll stop using
OL,14,Fsubstances."
OL,16,FDeputy Coles stressed that
OL,17,Fdecriminalising the drug would not
OL,18,Fmean legalising it.
OL,20,FHowever, not all government officials
OL,21,Fare on board with decriminalisation.
