OL,3,CProposition to decriminalise cannabis
OL,4,Cin Jersey for personal use
OL,6,FDeputy Kevin Lewis explained: "I'm all
OL,7,Fin favour of anything that a doctor
OL,8,Fprescribes, but I do fear that
OL,9,Fdecriminalising cannabis could send
OL,10,Fout the wrong message."
OL,12,FDeputy Coles believes roadside drug
OL,13,Ftesting kits would also be needed,
OL,14,Flike those in the UK, to ensure users
OL,15,Fdon't drive under the influence.
OL,17,FOther parts of Europe, including
OL,18,FGermany, Malta, and Luxembourg, have
OL,19,Fpartially decriminalised cannabis use.
