OL,4,Cin Jersey for personal use
OL,6,FJonas Wiening, a German journalist,
OL,7,Fsaid opinion is still very divided in
OL,8,Fhis country.
OL,10,FHe explained: "It's 50-50. People can
OL,11,Fbuy (cannabis) in an illegal way where
OL,12,Fthey don't know where it is coming
OL,13,Ffrom, so it's good to stop that.
OL,15,F"But on the other side, people argue
OL,16,Fthat it can be a gateway for other
OL,17,Fdrugs."
